{"lastModified":1765281724066,"uri":"c::8193426698::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: East Mediterranean / Croatia\n\nCharter Sunreef 50 in Croatia. The Sunreef 50 SWEET DREAMS luxury catamaran has superyacht quality in a compact package. As the smallest of the extensive range of Sunreef Yachts, she is an all-around sailing leisure yacht ideal for exclusive getaways, charter, and transoceanic adventures. Her clever bridge deck and superstructure design allow for a superior level of comfort onboard whereas the generous teak use, high bulwarks, and elegant lines underscore her modern, timeless style.","blueprint":{"name":"SWEET DREAMS","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::9bad4210-dc8c-11ef-b4d9-55db06f546db/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::94633830-dc8b-11ef-a2cf-23fd5dbcd30d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::94223790-dc8b-11ef-8b34-0b9b3a52ee9f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::94577860-dc8b-11ef-8b34-0b9b3a52ee9f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::9433c3c0-dc8b-11ef-8b34-0b9b3a52ee9f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::9456dc20-dc8b-11ef-8b34-0b9b3a52ee9f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::9458d7f0-dc8b-11ef-af51-b5434faff3cc/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::9463ad60-dc8b-11ef-8b34-0b9b3a52ee9f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::94633830-dc8b-11ef-8b34-0b9b3a52ee9f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::94