ak Deck"},{"label":"Bimini Top"}],"toys":[{"label":"Water skies for adults and kids"},{"label":"Wakeboard "},{"label":"Kneeboard"},{"label":"Towable Ring"},{"label":"Two SUP (stand-up-paddle)"},{"label":"Snorkeling Gear: Masks & flippers"},{"label":"Beach games"},{"label":"Floating Mates"}],"entertainment":["Sonos Surround 5.1","SAT Antenna","Speakers","TV Set & Satelite\t","DVD / Blueray player","Internet WIFi"],"tenders":["Highfield Sport 420 Rib with Honda BF60LRT outboard"]},"crew":[{"name":"Dino Slatki","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8193426698::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::bc5b78c0-d4f6-11f0-b2ea-313bea849059/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Dino Slatki, born in 1992 in Varaždin, Croatia. Dino Slatki spent most of his life on the sea. It started with fun sailing trips with the family as a little boy, then recreational sailing at first which turned into a passion and later a job. He completed his Yacht-Master 100 BT license in Zagreb, as well as D2 Basic Safety and GMDSS license. Dino graduated from the University of Kinesiology (human movement) exercise & sports sciences in Zagreb, where he majored in Sailing. He has been working as a skipper ever since. As a highly trained and experienced yachtsman, Dino has always been winning high\nplaudits from his clients for his friendly and sweet (as his surname Slatki says) character. He has a calm attitude to problem-solving, and his commitment to putting his clients’ interests first. Dino is a devoted husband and father of two, competent captain, approachable always, and will be as discrete or engaged as you wish him to be."},{"name":"Ariana Vukušić","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8193426698::vessel::7794a739-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::ceb09e10-d4f6-11f0-b2ea-313bea849059/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Ariana Vukišić was born and raised in Povlja on the island of Brač.\nFrom her early age she was drawn to the art of food preparation and boating, though her family business. It didn’t take long before she was pulled in and is still mesmerized by it.\nFluent in English, Ariana is happy to share with our guests her knowledge about Croatian history, art and nature. Being a visual person, Ariana makes everything prettier, weather it is the meals she prepares, drinks she serves or making the yacht clean and tidy.\nHer interests include cooking and exploring local cuisines. Ariana joined our team in 2021 as the stewardess/chef aboard s/y Sunreef 50 Solitaire and s/y Blessed, and quickly adjusted to the strict regime of living and working on the sea.\nShe is hard working and has eye for details. Ariana is extremely motivated to constantly develop her skills and grows professionally, customer satisfaction is what drives her to give her best performance.\nAriana feels the needs of her guests and stay invisible when required."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":1750000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":1750000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3400000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3400000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Until 26.04. From 27.09.","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-04-26T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-04-26T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-04-26T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-09-27T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-27T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-09-27T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-12-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","charterFee":1750000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":1750000,"amount":1750000,"conditions":"Weekly","taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.13}},{"item":"APA","conditions":"Weekly","quantity":1,"unitPrice":700000,"amount":700000}],"total":2450000,"subTotal":2450000,"totalTax":227500},"inclusionZones":[{"l